00:41:28,944 --> 00:41:31,742
that we didn't see the ones within.

672
00:41:31,847 --> 00:41:35,248
This place is tryin'
to change us, Gunn.

673
00:41:35,350 --> 00:41:37,250
We can't ever forget that.

674
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:42,686
Pretty damn good party though.
I'll see you tomorrow.

675
00:41:42,791 --> 00:41:45,589
Well, you know, today, but later.

676
00:41:45,694 --> 00:41:48,128
<i>- Oh, and your chair--</i>
- What?

677
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:51,222
Don't sit in it.
I already called Janitorial.

678
00:41:51,333 --> 00:41:53,631
Why can't I--

679
00:41:53,735 --> 00:41:57,262
You pissed in the big man's chair?
That's fantastic.

680
00:41:57,372 --> 00:41:59,306
Spike, can you please turn off
that warm fuzzy?

681
00:41:59,407 --> 00:42:02,103
What, the Lorne thing? Wore off.
I just think that's bloody fabulous.

682
00:42:02,210 --> 00:42:04,576
All right, guys. Good night.

683
00:42:04,679 --> 00:42:07,204
Let Lorne get some sleep, all right?

684
00:42:07,315 --> 00:42:09,442
Out.

685
00:42:09,551 --> 00:42:12,019
All right.Just this once.

686
00:42:14,956 --> 00:42:17,584
<i>[ Lorne Moans, Mumbles ]</i>

687
00:42:17,692 --> 00:42:19,887
I'm sorry.
[ Mumbling Continues ]

688
00:42:19,995 --> 00:42:22,463
Hey, it's okay, Lorne.

689
00:42:22,564 --> 00:42:25,328
-Just try to get some rest. Get some sleep.
- Mmm.

690
00:42:25,433 --> 00:42:29,597
Yeah. 'Cause it's-- it's hard to--

691
00:42:29,704 --> 00:42:32,172
It's hard bein'--
bein' the host of the party.

692
00:42:32,274 --> 00:42:34,242
Bein'--

693
00:42:34,342 --> 00:42:36,310
Stop tryin' to be.

694
00:43:27,896 --> 00:43:30,296
Grr! Arrgh!

